---
import LandingPage from '../../layouts/LandingPage.astro';
---
<LandingPage 
  title="ETA & ETD Forecasting" 
  description="Stop guessing. Get highly accurate predictions for vessel arrivals and departures using our machine learning powered ETA engine."
  ctaUrl="https://porttracker.co/forecast"
  ctaLabel="View Forecast"
>
  <div class="feature-block">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Machine Learning Predictions</h2>
      <p>We analyze historical port congestion, current vessel speeds, weather patterns, and specific berth availability to provide Estimated Times of Arrival (ETA) that are far more accurate than raw AIS broadcasts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🔮</div>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-block reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Terminal Planning Made Easy</h2>
      <p>With precise forecasting, terminal operators and stevedores can allocate resources perfectly. Reduce overtime costs and eliminate port bottlenecks by knowing exactly when the ship will truly be alongside.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">📅</div>
  </div>
</LandingPage>
